        "innerText": "1"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vibhāgenā"
      },
      "ti ",
      " sarūpavibhāgena. Adiṭṭhaṃ jotīyati etāyāti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "adiṭṭhajotanā"
      },
      ". Diṭṭhaṃ saṃsandīyati etāyāti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "diṭṭhasaṃsandanā,"
      },
      " saṃsandanaṃ cettha sākacchāvasena vinicchayakaraṇaṃ. Vimati chijjati etāyāti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vimaticchedanā"
      },
      ". Anumatiyā pucchā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "anumatipucchā"
      },
      ". ‘‘Taṃ kiṃ maññathā’’ti hi kā tumhākaṃ anumatīti anumati pucchitā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kathetukamyatā"
      },
      "ti kathetukamyatāya."
    ],
    "innerText": "1.Vibhāgenāti sarūpavibhāgena. Adiṭṭhaṃ jotīyati etāyāti adiṭṭhajotanā. Diṭṭhaṃ saṃsandīyati etāyāti diṭṭhasaṃsandanā, saṃsandanaṃ cettha sākacchāvasena vinicchayakaraṇaṃ. Vimati chijjati etāyāti vimaticchedanā. Anumatiyā pucchā anumatipucchā. ‘‘Taṃ kiṃ maññathā’’ti hi kā tumhākaṃ anumatīti anumati pucchitā. Kathetukamyatāti kathetukamyatāya."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘Harīyanti etehī’’"
      },
      "tiādinā karaṇādhikaraṇakattubhāvakammasādhanānaṃ vasena ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "hāra"
      },
      "-saddassa atthaṃ vatvā sadisakappanāvasena dassetuṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘hārā viyā’’"
      },
      "tiādi vuttaṃ. Puna ganthakaraṇādiatthena ganthādisaddānaṃ viya hārakaraṇādiatthena hārasaddasiddhiṃ dassetuṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘hārayantī’’"
      },
      "tiādimāha. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘Haraṇato, ramaṇato cā’’"
      },
      "ti iminā manoharā manoramā cete saṃvaṇṇanāvisesāti dasseti."
    ],
    "innerText": "‘‘Harīyanti etehī’’tiādinā karaṇādhikaraṇakattubhāvakammasādhanānaṃ vasena hāra-saddassa atthaṃ vatvā sadisakappanāvasena dassetuṃ ‘‘hārā viyā’’tiādi vuttaṃ. Puna ganthakaraṇādiatthena ganthādisaddānaṃ viya hārakaraṇādiatthena hārasaddasiddhiṃ dassetuṃ ‘‘hārayantī’’tiādimāha. ‘‘Haraṇato, ramaṇato cā’’ti iminā manoharā manoramā cete saṃvaṇṇanāvisesāti dasseti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
