    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Anuppavesīyantī"
      },
      "ti ",
      " avagāhīyanti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Samādhīyantī"
      },
      "ti pariharīyanti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vinā vikappenā"
      },
      "ti jāti sāmaññaṃ, bhedo sāmaññaṃ, sambandho sāmaññantiādinā padatthantarabhāvavikappanamantarena."
    ],
    "innerText": "Anuppavesīyantīti avagāhīyanti. Samādhīyantīti pariharīyanti. Vinā vikappenāti jāti sāmaññaṃ, bhedo sāmaññaṃ, sambandho sāmaññantiādinā padatthantarabhāvavikappanamantarena."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Padaṭṭhānādimukhenā"
      },
      "ti padaṭṭhānavevacanabhāvanāpahānamukhena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kecī"
      },
      "ti padaṭṭhānaparikkhāraāvaṭṭaparivattanapaññattiotaraṇe sandhāya vadati."
    ],
    "innerText": "Padaṭṭhānādimukhenāti padaṭṭhānavevacanabhāvanāpahānamukhena. Kecīti padaṭṭhānaparikkhāraāvaṭṭaparivattanapaññattiotaraṇe sandhāya vadati."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "2"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sambandho"
      },
      "ti hetuphalabhāvayogo. Tathābhūtānañhi dhammānaṃ ekasantānasiddhatā ekattanayo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vibhāgo"
      },
      " satipi nesaṃ hetuphalabhāve vibhattasabhāvatā. Añño eva hi hetu, aññaṃ phalanti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Byāpāraviraho"
      },
      " nirīhatā. Na hi hetuphalānaṃ evaṃ hoti ‘‘ahaṃ imaṃ nibbattemi, imināhaṃ nibbatto’’ti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Anurūpaphalatā"
      },
      " paccayuppannānaṃ paccayānukūlatā. Samūhādiṃ ",
      " upādāya lokasaṅketasiddhā vohāramattatā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sammutisabhāvo"
      },
      ". Pathavīphassādīnaṃ kakkhaḷaphusanādilakkhaṇaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "paramatthasabhāvo"
      },
      ". Ayañhettha saṅkhepo – yasmiṃ bhinne, itarāpohe vā cittena katena tathā buddhi, idaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sammutisaccaṃ"
      },
      " yathā ghaṭe, sasambhārajale ca, tabbipariyāyena ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "paramatthasacca"
      },
      "nti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paramatthasaccappaṭivedhāyā"
      },
      "ti nibbānādhigamāya."
    ],
    "innerText": "2.Sambandhoti hetuphalabhāvayogo. Tathābhūtānañhi dhammānaṃ ekasantānasiddhatā ekattanayo. Vibhāgo satipi nesaṃ hetuphalabhāve vibhattasabhāvatā. Añño eva hi hetu, aññaṃ phalanti. Byāpāraviraho nirīhatā. Na hi hetuphalānaṃ evaṃ hoti ‘‘ahaṃ imaṃ nibbattemi, imināhaṃ nibbatto’’ti. Anurūpaphalatā paccayuppannānaṃ paccayānukūlatā. Samūhādiṃ upādāya lokasaṅketasiddhā vohāramattatā sammutisabhāvo. Pathavīphassādīnaṃ kakkhaḷaphusanādilakkhaṇaṃ paramatthasabhāvo. Ayañhettha saṅkhepo – yasmiṃ bhinne, itarāpohe vā cittena katena tathā buddhi, idaṃ sammutisaccaṃ yathā ghaṭe, sasambhārajale ca, tabbipariyāyena paramatthasaccanti. Paramatthasaccappaṭivedhāyāti nibbānādhigamāya."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Anto"
      },
      "ti abbhantaro. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Padhānāvayavenā"
      },
      "ti mūlabhāvena. ‘‘Nandī dukkhassa mūla’’ntiādīsu (ma. ni. 1.13) taṇhā ‘‘nandī’’ti vuttā. ‘‘Saṅgāme ca nandiṃ caratī’’tiādīsu pamodoti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘taṇhāya, pamodassa vā’’"
      },
      "ti."
    ],
    "innerText": "Antoti abbhantaro. Padhānāvayavenāti mūlabhāvena. ‘‘Nandī dukkhassa mūla’’ntiādīsu (ma. ni. 1.13) taṇhā ‘‘nandī’’ti vuttā. ‘‘Saṅgāme ca nandiṃ caratī’’tiādīsu pamodoti āha ‘‘taṇhāya, pamodassa vā’’ti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "3"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Jātibhedato"
      },
      "ti kusalā, akusalāti imasmā visesā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Yujjantī"
      },
      "ti ettha hetuattho antonīto veditabboti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘yojīyantī’’"
      },
      "ti. Kehi yojīyanti? Saṃvaṇṇanakehīti adhippāyo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Yujjantī"
      },
      "ti vā yuttā honti, tehi samānayogakkhamā taggahaṇeneva gahitā hontīti attho tadekaṭṭhabhāvato. Imasmiṃ atthe ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘navahi padehī’’"
      },
      "ti sahayoge karaṇavacanaṃ, purimasmiṃ karaṇe. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘Ete kho’’"
      },
      "ti ca pāṭho. Tattha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "kho"
      },
      "-saddassa padapūraṇatā, avadhāraṇatthatā vā veditabbā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ete evā"
      },
      "ti ete taṇhādayo eva, na ito aññeti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aṭṭhāraseva"
      },
      " na tato uddhaṃ, adho vāti. Purimasmiṃ pakkhe mūlapadantarābhāvo, dutiyasmiṃ tesaṃ anūnādhikatā dīpitā hoti."
    ],
    "innerText": "3.Jātibhedatoti kusalā, akusalāti imasmā visesā. Yujjantīti ettha hetuattho antonīto veditabboti āha ‘‘yojīyantī’’ti. Kehi yojīyanti? Saṃvaṇṇanakehīti adhippāyo. Yujjantīti vā yuttā honti, tehi samānayogakkhamā taggahaṇeneva gahitā hontīti attho tadekaṭṭhabhāvato. Imasmiṃ atthe ‘‘navahi padehī’’ti sahayoge karaṇavacanaṃ, purimasmiṃ karaṇe. ‘‘Ete kho’’ti ca pāṭho. Tattha kho-saddassa padapūraṇatā, avadhāraṇatthatā vā veditabbā. Ete evāti ete taṇhādayo eva, na ito aññeti attho. Aṭṭhāraseva na tato uddhaṃ, adho vāti. Purimasmiṃ pakkhe mūlapadantarābhāvo, dutiyasmiṃ tesaṃ anūnādhikatā dīpitā hoti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Uddesavāravaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  }
